Review: Misterinya seru banget diikutin tapi masih bingung aja main core story nya ini emang berfokus pada romansa jeng yah sama raja atau persaingan bisnis kreteknya. Kalau berdasarkan judul gadis kretek, harusnya lebih ditonjolin persaingan bisnis kreteknya ya dibanding romansanya. Tbh ga baca bukunya tapi filmnya menarik 👏

It's really not given a pause, the plot runs so fast and it won't feel like it has reached the end of the story. But it's still fun to enjoy. Even the villain was made to disappear even though at the beginning it was made so cruel and terrible, this is quite unfortunate. It can be seen that another purpose of this film is to be a prologue for a new generation of avengers teams and superhero entities in other universes 😆👍

Teror pocong satu demi satu menghantui sebuah desa, entah apa penyebabnya apa karna si “pamali” itu kah? Wabah yg datang pun belum begitu jelas how & why nya? Apa karna si “pamali” itu? Saya rasa tidak sesimple itu. Endingnya pun anti klimaks padahal teror di awal ke tengah serem wkwk
The atmosphere still manages to make sitting uncomfortable with various techniques, the plot is also easy to follow, unlike the first messy film. In the end kawa-kawa is still over power here 😜

Randomising emotions from the beginning to the end of the film. I feel like I want to have Doraemon's door and then save the poor Hwang Sun-woo 😭👍 It's amazing to have knowledge and mental maturity at a young age for the size of an astonot. If I give up and panic attack 😂
I don't know I lost my life in an insidious film where its predecessor was so memorable and made sitting in the cinema seat uncomfortable and the after taste was quite paranoid.

This DC film must be admitted that this DC film is one of the best DC films. Resetting the DCEU with the flash as a first step is the right decision. Like giving an idea of how the possibilities are if we try to tinker with time and stories like resetting the DCEU, it is felt that there will be a challenge in itself. I really like the concept of the multiverse built by this flash 💯The characterisations and…

Appreciation first because the premise offered is still strong about his family just like the first film. Apart from the slightly eccentric shazam jokes, the supporting actors and villains are not given the right portion. The standard scene of fighting is also less exciting
The script is simple but how aesthetic the blood-filled action is with the acting of the actor & actress who are very total.
The story of the galaxy guardian's last journey that is so warm, meaningful, entertaining, emotional, sad, happiness,tears, happiness, tears, …..🥲
